  ],
  "remarks": "TV-Novosti is a Russian-government-linked media organisation. It is funded from the federal budget of the Russian Federation. Through its subordinate media outlets, including RT, it has consistently spread pro-Kremlin propaganda and disinformation, and supported Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Through its content, RT spreads false narratives of the Russian regime to undermine Ukraine and is thus supporting a large-scale disinformation campaign to erode international support for Ukraine.",
